listings.comment: Ali has done an exceptional work. I am very happy to find such a designer and developer. I will 100% hire him again for such jobs in the future. Eternally grateful. He definitely went above and beyond and helped me issues outside of the scope of this gig.
His willingness to work with you is what made me give him 5 stars. It took quite a bit of back and forth to get things to my liking but he was always quick and did exactly as I asked. Great work!

Ali is absolutely AMAZING! I am beyond grateful that I found him!! 

He did the most incredible job with my website! He is easy to work with, was quick and diligent, paid attention to detail, was great with implementing my feedback, it is obvious that he wants to make sure that his clients are happy and holds their projects to a high standard, and he goes the extra mile to make everything the best that he can!

I will definitely be hiring him again for all of my website needs, and highly recommend him to anyone else looking for support with their website!

Ali was great to work with and FAST. He was a clear communicator and very easy to understand. He was intent on understanding the vision for the project and as a result, edits were kept to a minimum. In those areas where we had changes he did them promptly. We will absolutely work with him again.

Amazing experience, was here for me at every step of the way and incredibly helpful. Need a call? He's here for you. Have a question? He's here for you. Difficult to find people as helpful as him. Definitely recommend for anyone
